<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 13:24:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Winklevosses 向饱受打击的 Gemini 交易所投资 1 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/winklevosses-invest-100-million-in-battered-gemini-exchange</link><description>创立 Gemini Space Station Inc. 的亿万富翁双胞胎泰勒·文克莱沃斯 (Tyler Winklevoss) 和卡梅伦·温克莱沃斯 (Cameron Winklevoss) 对这家亏损的加密货币交易所进行了 1 亿美元的“战略投资”。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyH6RCEPUEe0/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 21:11:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/winklevosses-invest-100-million-in-battered-gemini-exchange</guid></item><item><title>代币化正在金融领域最不性感的角落被拥抱</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-14/tokenization-is-catching-on-in-the-least-sexy-corner-of-finance-repo</link><description>区块链在回购市场中的使用正在蓬勃发展。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i5Bcso_KIQgM/v18/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-14/tokenization-is-catching-on-in-the-least-sexy-corner-of-finance-repo</guid></item><item><title>加密货币亿万富翁加入投资者的行列，押注委内瑞拉高风险以获得巨额回报</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/crypto-billionaire-ehrsam-joins-risky-bet-on-venezuela-revival</link><description>美国加密货币亿万富翁 Fred Ehrsam 已成为吸引委内瑞拉的最引人注目、最引人注目的外国投资者之一，他押注这个饱受制裁的国家可能会在其遭受重创的经济重新开放时提供巨额回报。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCc_7HRlPruQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 18:54:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/crypto-billionaire-ehrsam-joins-risky-bet-on-venezuela-revival</guid></item><item><title>随着加密货币市场监管法案的推进，比特币突破 80,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/bitcoin-stalls-as-crypto-gains-ground-in-washington-wall-street</link><description>参议院银行委员会经过数月的谈判提出了具有里程碑意义的美国数字资产市场结构法案后，比特币价格攀升至 80,000 美元以上。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipACoh5nEXcw/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 14:58:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-14/bitcoin-stalls-as-crypto-gains-ground-in-washington-wall-street</guid></item></channel></rss>